  "description": "Make Creepers ignite only within your field of view.",
  "body": "  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'trebuchet ms', geneva, sans-serif; color: #2dc26b; font-size: 36px;\"><strong>Creeper Backguard</strong></span></p><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #e03e2d;\">Server and Client side</span></h3> <h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Make Creepers ignite only within your field of view.</span></h2>\n\n<div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Are you tired of losing all your precious items because of those sneaky Creepers that always catch you off guard?</span></p></div>\n\n <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media2.giphy.com/media/v1.Y2lkPTc5MGI3NjExMmg3N3d0bnFpMDJ4N20yZXBjYW1qZ3Uwc2UwaTlyZmlvN3NyZm02cyZlcD12MV9pbnRlcm5hbF9naWZfYnlfaWQmY3Q9Zw/Xg2x4QpXYB3w9M18aE/giphy.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\"></span></p> <p style=\"text-align: center;\">**Dynamic FOV support <span style=\"color: #2dc26b;\">[1.21.x]</span>**</p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://media0.giphy.com/media/v1.Y2lkPTc5MGI3NjExem9zemQ3OHp5Y21ud2c2b3N2cmpoN3NhZ24xeW14YmJ4Nm5zcTBkeiZlcD12MV9pbnRlcm5hbF9naWZfYnlfaWQmY3Q9Zw/h8h7yLW95FKOwJioQB/giphy.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\"></span></p> \n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><hr></div>",
